OL,3,CThe Abbeystead survivor raising money
OL,4,Cin memory of those he lost forty years
OL,5,Cago
OL,7,FITV News' Victoria Grime went to meet
OL,8,FJohn at the site of the explosion.
OL,10,FA survivor of the 1984 Abbeystead
OL,11,FDisaster who raised more than #36,000
OL,12,Fin memory of those who lost their
OL,13,Flives has been nominated for a Pride
OL,14,Fof Britain award.
OL,16,FJohn Holmes, from St Michael's on Wyre
OL,17,Fnear Garstang, took on a 30 mile walk
OL,18,Fin 2024 to mark 40 years since the
OL,19,Fdisaster which killed 16 people
OL,20,Fincluding an 11-year-old boy.
