OL,3,CThe Abbeystead survivor raising money
OL,4,Cin memory of those he lost forty years
OL,5,Cago
OL,7,FJohn had been among 44 locals who had
OL,8,Fbeen invited to take a tour of
OL,9,FAbbeystead pumping station on 23 May
OL,10,F1984.
OL,12,FHe was inside the underground building
OL,13,Fwhen a large explosion, later found to
OL,14,Fhave been caused by a build-up of
OL,15,Fmethane gas, destroyed the building.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
