OL,3,CThe Abbeystead survivor raising money
OL,4,Cin memory of those he lost forty years
OL,5,Cago
OL,7,FMore than four decades on, John's
OL,8,Fphysical scars may have healed but the
OL,9,Fmemories of that night will never
OL,10,Fleave him.
OL,12,FSpeaking at the site of the explosion,
OL,13,FJohn said: "It's always difficult to
OL,14,Fcome here, and whenever you speak to
OL,15,Fanyone about it you just break down.
OL,17,F"40 years later it's still there in
OL,18,Fmost (survivors). I cope very well I
OL,19,Fthink, but last year I thought it's 40
OL,20,Fyears since Abbeystead, and I'm going
OL,21,Fto walk."
