OL,3,CThe Abbeystead survivor raising money
OL,4,Cin memory of those he lost forty years
OL,5,Cago
OL,7,FIn January 2024, John decided he would
OL,8,Ftake on a two-day 30-mile walk across
OL,9,FLancashire to raise money for the
OL,10,Fburns unit that treated him after the
OL,11,Fexplosion.
OL,13,FJohn's walk raised more than #20,000
OL,14,Ffor the hospice, and since then he has
OL,15,Ftaken on a number of challenges and
OL,16,Forganised more fundraising events.
OL,18,FOn 7 June 2025, John took on his
OL,19,Fbiggest challenge yet when he walked
OL,20,Fup Mount Snowdon alongside many of the
OL,21,Fnurses who work on the burns unit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
