OL,3,CThe Abbeystead survivor raising money
OL,4,Cin memory of those he lost forty years
OL,5,Cago
OL,7,FAltogether John has raised more than
OL,8,F#36,000 for the Royal Preston
OL,9,FHospital's burn unit, which has been
OL,10,Fused to purchase vital medical
OL,11,Fequipment.
OL,13,FThe unit is now equipped with a
OL,14,Fcosmetic chair and makeup, making it
OL,15,Fpossible to apply camouflage to
OL,16,Fpatients' burns and scars. Staff have
OL,17,Falso been able to purchase a sewing
OL,18,Fmachine, meaning they can make
OL,19,Fpressure garments on site rather than
OL,20,Fwaiting for them to be delivered from
OL,21,Fother sites.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
