OL,3,CThe Abbeystead survivor raising money
OL,4,Cin memory of those he lost forty years
OL,5,Cago
OL,7,FMarcia Roach, Lead Nurse at the Royal
OL,8,FPreston Hospital said: "The
OL,9,Fpsychological impact of any scarring
OL,10,Fis obviously horrendous and just to
OL,11,Fhave the treatment they're having is
OL,12,Fgoing to make a massive difference, so
OL,13,Fwe can't thank John enough."
OL,15,FOne staff nurse who knows just how
OL,16,Fvital the equipment can be is Cathy
OL,17,FChapple, who was working on the ward
OL,18,Fin the immediate aftermath of the
OL,19,Fexplosion.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
