OL,3,CThe Abbeystead survivor raising money
OL,4,Cin memory of those he lost forty years
OL,5,Cago
OL,7,FCathy said: "I'll never forget that
OL,8,Ftime. I can still see the faces,
OL,9,Fremember the names. A lady I looked
OL,10,Fafter... She was beautiful, and we
OL,11,Fthought she would be alright. But she
OL,12,Fdied, and I've never forgotten her.
OL,14,F"I can still remember the night it
OL,15,Fhappened. I still remember everything
OL,16,Fabout it."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
