OL,5,Cago
OL,7,FWhen asked what being nominated for
OL,8,Fthe Pride of Britain Fundraiser of the
OL,9,FYear award means to him, John said: "I
OL,10,Fhope it means a lot for the hospital
OL,11,Fand the charity, not me.
OL,13,F"I just didn't want people to forget
OL,14,FAbbeystead. I've got to be here to
OL,15,Flive their life. Everything I've done
OL,16,Fis for them."
