OL,7,FPride of Britain Awards celebrate the
OL,8,Fachievements of truly remarkable
OL,9,Fpeople who make our world a better
OL,10,Fplace.
OL,12,FNominated by the public, the winners
OL,13,Fare from all walks of life, of all
OL,14,Fages, and from all over the country.
OL,15,FTheir achievements are awe-inspiring
OL,16,Fand a lesson to us all.
